9F%E9%81%8E%E5%A5%BD%E6%AF%8F%E4%B8%80%E6%97%A5%E3%80%8D</a><br />\n<br />\n個子不高，身型單薄，長髮被剷短，劉家棟是反送中運動首位阻差辦公罪成的社工。不涉暴力、不涉蒙面、不涉拒捕，但被判即時監禁一年，為同類控罪刑期較重的案件，對他來說十分愕然。他在獄中認識了一名手足，同一日向高院申請保釋上訴，二人坐著同一輛囚車出發，相約在法庭外見，但最終一人成功一人失敗，剩下一人獨自回程，重返荔枝角收押所。在法院臭格內，曾有這一幕：<br />\n<br />\n他搖頭，我點頭。他對著我笑，然後被帶上囚車。我望著他背影，大叫撐住啊！"},{"pid":"f92278438fbdbe0a08741b202745ecf19c95a7a9","tid":2102803,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T18:09:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4ae4aa7f4c124c2a09d5dfcab3f1868c7b224f3","tid":2102803,"uid":250948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T18:09:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb39007cdc15cca25fc41629577833ea61345cc0","tid":2102803,"uid":67237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T18:09:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5cd8f1cc09d25e49dbafbeb6cc23915c26704339","tid":2102803,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a4ae4aa7f4c124c2a09d5dfcab3f1868c7b224f3","tid":2102803,"uid":250948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T18:09:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T18:10:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=